OSTCProtocol070511
public class OSTCProtocol080115
extends AbstractOSTCProtocol

Same Protocol as 1.0 Versions, but it has a function to reset DecoInformation and a function to read only EEPROM values rather than the whole profile memory.

Author:
Pascal Pellmont
